message.body: So how was Shakespeare? Clark Park has sure come a long way since i used to hang out there. What other erudite activities have you been up to this wknd?
Oh, not too much. I'm going on a bike ride today I think. You?
Catching up on some volunteer work, ultimate frisbee, then watching the new Wolverine movie with a friend. How long of a bike ride are you going on?
